README

Problem setup for a uniform density cube, configured to accept some turbulent
velocity pattern.  A direct descendant of the Cube simulation.
Used for some troubleshooting circa March-April 2019.

Simple code to generate cube velocity pattern can be found in the repo
`flash_interface`.

If you are using this simulation problem, you should carefully confirm that the
simulation does what you expect.  The problem compiles successfully (2019 June
01) but has not been tested by execution.  The successful setup call is:

    ./setup Cube_Velocity -a -3d +usm +gravMgrid +rayPE +HandCnew +amuseSinksAndStars
    +amuseWind +enerinj +supportPPMupwind +pm4dev -maxblocks=300 +cube16
    -objdir=objectcube
